I"=<h1 id="general-principles">General Principles</h1>
<ul>
  <li>Many patients undergoing anesthesia will experience post-operative nausea and vomiting</li>
  <li>Anti-emetic medications are given routinely during anesthesia.</li>
  <li>Combining agents of different classes reduces side effects and improves anti-emetic action</li>
</ul>

<h1 id="clinical-pathway">Clinical Pathway</h1>

