<h1 id="risk-factors-for-nausea">Risk Factors for Nausea</h1>
<h2 id="patient-risk-factors--apfel-score-">Patient Risk Factors – Apfel Score <sup id="fnref:1" role="doc-noteref"><a href="#fn:1" class="footnote" rel="footnote">1</a></sup></h2>
<ul>
  <li>Female</li>
  <li>Non-smoker</li>
  <li>history of PONV/motion sickness</li>
  <li>post-operative opioids</li>
</ul>

<table>
  <thead>
    <tr>
      <th>Apfel Score Points</th>
      <th>Risk of PONV</th>
    </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
    <tr>
      <td>0</td>
      <td>10%</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>1</td>
      <td>20%</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>2</td>
      <td>40%</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>3</td>
      <td>60%</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>4</td>
      <td>80%</td>
    </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>

<h2 id="surgical-risk-factors">Surgical Risk Factors</h2>
<ul>
  <li>Cholecystectomy</li>
  <li>laparoscopic</li>
  <li>gynecologic</li>
</ul>

<h2 id="anesthetic-risk-factors">Anesthetic Risk Factors</h2>
<ul>
  <li>Duration of anesthesia</li>
  <li>use of volatile anesthetics / nitrous oxide</li>
</ul>

<h1 id="medications-to-prevent-ponv">Medications to Prevent PONV</h1>

<h2 id="5-ht3-antagonists">5-HT<sub>3</sub> Antagonists</h2>
<p>[[Ondansetron]]</p>

<h2 id="antidopaminergics">Antidopaminergics</h2>
<p>[[Haloperidol]]
[[Metoclopromide]]</p>

<h2 id="nk1-receptor-antagonists">NK1 Receptor Antagonists</h2>
<p>[[Aprepitant]]</p>

<h2 id="corticosteroids">Corticosteroids</h2>
<p>[[Dexamethasone]]</p>

